Feature: Hg. Get Archive List

Background:
	Given test user login
		And these settings
			| UseCategories | UseCurrency |
			| true          | true        |
		And I have two accounts
		And I have a category

Scenario: Hg01. Unlogged user
	Given I have no logged user (logoff)
	When get archive list
	Then I will receive this core error: Uninvited

Scenario: Hg02. User marked for deletion
	Given the user is marked for deletion
	When get archive list
	Then I will receive this core error: UserDeleted

Scenario: Hg03. User requested wipe
	Given the user asked data wipe
	When get archive list
	Then I will receive this core error: UserAskedWipe

Scenario: Hg04. Without sign last contract
	Given there is a new contract
	When get archive list
	Then I will receive this core error: NotSignedLastContract

Scenario: Hg05. No archives
	When get archive list
	Then I will receive no core error
		And the archive list will be
			| Lines | Status  |

